    * Draft
    * Starred (by whom?)
* Reply button
    * Autocomplete username from global list of contacts.
* Labels (have a label class per user)
    * Inbox
    * Archive
    * Trash
* Sent Mails (i.e. Am I the sender of this?)  (implied from sender)

## Phase II: Day of MessageDat
